        {
          "id": "N_ENTER",
          "type": "npc_line",
          "speakerId": "NARRATOR",
          "text": "The records hallway is built to erase urgency. (pause)\nBeige paint. Metal frames. (pause)\nSoft-close doors that keep arguments inside. (pause)\n\nThe pneumatic tube station doesn\u2019t match that philosophy. (pause)\nIts indicator lamp is lit\u2014steady, patient. Like it\u2019s been waiting to be acknowledged. (pause)\n\nIn the receiver tray: a dot-matrix printout. Still curled from the rollers.",
          "next": "N_MAIN_MENU"
        },
